              class="dropdown-item"
              style="display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;"
              href="https://github.com/riiconnect24/RiiConnect24-Patcher/releases"
              ><div style="transform:translate(-5px, 0);">
                <img
                  alt="RC24 Logo"
                  loading="lazy"
